Rich in healthy fats, vitamin E, and plant protein, hazelnuts support glowing skin, long-lasting energy, and heart-healthy nutrition. Enjoy them straight from the pouch, blend into nut butter, or sprinkle over breakfast bowls for a delicious nutrient boost.

fields.name: Blanched almonds
fields.description:
Our blanched almonds boast a clean, creamy ivory colour with a smooth, velvety surface — created naturally when the almonds are gently steamed to remove their skins. Their light, uniform tone is a hallmark of premium-grade nuts, ensuring consistent quality in every pack.

Sustainably sourced from trusted growers who prioritise ethical farming and water-responsible cultivation, these almonds are harvested with respect for the land and local communities. Each batch is carefully selected to support environmentally conscious agriculture, ensuring freshness, purity, and long-term sustainability.

Beyond their beautiful pale-gold colour, blanched almonds are packed with health benefits. They’re naturally rich in vitamin E, magnesium, healthy fats, and plant-based protein — supporting skin health, energy levels, and overall wellbeing. Their gentle flavour and nutrient density make them perfect for snacking, baking, blending, or adding a wholesome boost to your favourite dishes.

Pure, sustainable, and nourishing — these blanched almonds are a staple for every healthy pantry.
